        %p.epsilon I'm a Front-end Developer with over 4 years professional experience. I have an eye for detail, an appreciation of minimal design and a desire to continually improve my abilities.
        %p.epsilon Click through the tabs below to read a little about my core skill sets and approach to web development.
  .tabbed-content
    %ul.tabbed-content-nav{ role: "tablist" }
